-----CHAPTER 2: Getting Started with Scratch-----

1. Scratch is a VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY simple Language to learn, its made for kids even babies
2. to learn Scratch look it up on the youtube turtorial, im not a teacher
3. now if you know the basics of Scratch, you can continue!
4. Scroll down to The BOTTOM of the Sprites on the bottom right of your screen
5. you can see, theres a Sprite called Template Skill
6. inside that, you will the lots of yellow windows and its the "Build-in tutorial"!
7. you can read those but DONT change any if inputs and the thing that i DONT allow to change
8. once you understand, you can go to the next chapter
